description: Closed and baked pizza, stuffed with cheese, tomato sauce and different ingredients, an Italian classic!
Italian Christmas sweet bread with fruits configured and raisins, a traditional gift in Italy.
Italian pork salami with herbs and spices, a perfect accompaniment for sausage tables.
Delicious Italian Durum wheat paste, ideal for traditional pasta plates.
Italian classic dessert with coffee sponge cake, mascarpone and cocoa powder.
Italian incoming with eggplants, tomato, celery, capers and vinegar, a mixture of flavors.
The famous Italian cheese, matured for months to obtain its unique and rich flavor.
Classic Italian pizza with tomato, fresh mozzarella and basil.
Pork sausages seasoned with herbs and spices, perfect for snacks.
Fresh sardines in olive oil, a delicious and healthy bite.
